In re Edson’s Will. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Proceeding for the probate of the will of Mary A. Edson, deceased. From the decree entered, Marmont B. Edson appeals.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion denied.
